<li id="cite_note-80"><b><a href="#cite_ref-80" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFThompson2007">Thompson, Jody (8 January 2007). <a href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/6230201.stm" class="external text" title="http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/6230201.stm" rel="nofollow">"Sixty things about David Bowie"</a>. (No. 35): BBC News<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/6230201.stm" class="external free" title="http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/6230201.stm" rel="nofollow">http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/6230201.stm</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-01-12</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Sixty+things+about+David+Bowie&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Thompson&amp;rft.aufirst=Jody&amp;rft.au=Thompson%2C+Jody&amp;rft.date=8+January+2007&amp;rft.pub=%28No.+35%29%3A+BBC+News&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.bbc.co.uk%2F2%2Fhi%2Fentertainment%2F6230201.stm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:David_Bowie"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
